---
title: Golden Pumpkin, Chorizo & Israeli Couscous Medley with Hazelnuts & Plant-Based Basil Pesto Mayo
description: Quick and easy, that’s the best kind of dinner. Roast the pumpkin in our Aussie spice blend then whip up a fluffy couscous with tasty bites of chorizo and have it ready to be gobbled down in no time at all. Top it off with a plant-based basil pesto mayo to ensure there won’t be any crumbs left.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/golden-kumara-israeli-couscous-salad-6419b452.jpg
